code: @Override protected TypeSerializer<?>[] getNestedSerializers(CRowSerializer outerSerializer) {     return new TypeSerializer[] { outerSerializer.rowSerializer() }. }

@Override protected CRowSerializer createOuterSerializerWithNestedSerializers(TypeSerializer<?>[] nestedSerializers) {     @SuppressWarnings("unchecked")     TypeSerializer<Row> rowSerializer = (TypeSerializer<Row>) nestedSerializers[0].     return new CRowSerializer(rowSerializer). }
